{
  "stem": "15962.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So it was-- that's why I say they were very different.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The population was scared of the Russians and was running into the American zone because of rapes and, and robberies and-- after all, the Russians really suffered from the Germans and Austrians terribly.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They devastated their country and killed the population.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So the Russians were not wearing white gloves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] From Wiener Neustadt, there were no trains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we had to walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We formed groups.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And not quite sure whether we were guided here and there by a Russian soldier or how we were guided.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But it took several days to reach Slovakia, the capital of Slovakia, Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We slept by the roadside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We carried whatever we could, mostly stuff that the Americans gave us, some food, some soap, and just rudimentary stuff.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my memory is of the countryside being trampled by [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] horses.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The Russians were literally taking horses and cattle and chasing them towards the east.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I mean, they were just taking everything that they could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And that sticks in my mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I think there were some fruit trees, that we were eating some fruit on the side of the road and that we were pretty exhausted and advanced very slowly.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "When we reached the Danube, all the bridges were destroyed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And the Americans set up a pontoon bridge.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I recall crossing the pontoon bridge into Bratislava and being ushered into a refugee center where we were registered and sent to get a shower.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And again, everybody was afraid of contagious diseases.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So we were sent for fumigation time and again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Local people.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
